import "date"
from(bucket: "radem")
  |> range(start: date.sub(d: 10m, from: v.timeRangeStart), stop:date.add(d: 10m, to: v.timeRangeStop))
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "protons"
  )
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: true)

from(bucket: "juice_trajectory")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "sun_dist_au" or
    r._measurement == "earth_dist_au" or
    r._measurement == "mars_dist_au" or
    r._measurement == "jupiter_dist_au"
  )
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: true)
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_value", "_measurement"])
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
    _time: r._time,
    _value: r._value,
    _measurement: 
      if r._measurement == "sun_dist_au" then "Sun"
      else if r._measurement == "earth_dist_au" then "Earth"
      else if r._measurement == "mars_dist_au" then "Mars"
      else if r._measurement == "jupiter_dist_au" then "Jupiter"
      else "???"
  }))

from(bucket: "juice_trajectory")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "sun_ra" or
    r._measurement == "sun_dec"
  )
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: true)
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_value", "_measurement"])
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
    _time: r._time,
    _value: r._value,
    _measurement: 
      if r._measurement == "sun_ra" then "Right Ascension"
      else "Declination"
  }))
